{"tid":1351563,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"政府的壓力，中共，商家，罷工罷市","createTime":"2019-07-22T15:45:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T16:47:45.000Z","uid":279357,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"20343fc8c993e9a6331356c85bac8a03e8e2fc7a","tid":1351563,"uid":279357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T15:45:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><br />\n要好利用社會呢種恐怖嘅氣氛<br />\n市民大眾出外都覺得生命受到威脅<br />\n咁樣又點樣可能返到工生活到<br />\n響公司又怕冇保險我車又怕俾人打<br />\n係呢個時候係咪真真正正<br />\n需要諗下係咪罷工罷市呢<br />\n警察用暗黑手段令我哋市民有壓力<br />\n我哋係咪要商家呢俾返壓力政府<br />\n今日只係某D地區休半日市<br />\n商家已經頂唔住啦<br />\n如果將呢一個感覺延續落去<br />\n咁樣政府就會有更大嘅壓力<br />\n中央用警察警察用黑社會<br />\n我哋都用市場用商家係畀返壓力政府<br />\n我哋嘅籌碼並唔多<br />\n無論中聯辦國徽花幾多次<br />\n上環嘅兄弟姊妹中幾多子彈<br />\n元朗嘅香港市民受到幾大嘅傷害<br />\n都未必如香港停頓一日嘅影響大<br />\n但係商家嘅壓力就一定有力<br />\n嘅時候認真諗下點樣搞罷工罷市<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"edf99dcd2e717043ac29acac93de73569911da94","tid":1351563,"uid":279357,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T15:48:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">希望罷工罷市<br />\n可以令到我哋嘅義士<br />\n唔需要再去食子彈<br />\n受更加多嘅傷害<br />\n亦都唔使我哋嘅市民<br />\n再去承受無謂嘅恐懼同埋傷害<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">罷工罷市</span></span>"},{"pid":"253b40defe4cc8408fe129f5cdaf5953f7468e29","tid":1351563,"uid":266653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:02:23.000Z","msg":"繼續推<br />\n<br />\n西上環事件整合 求更多新聞同義士消息 推上去 唔好俾元朗事件淹沒！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1351169\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1351169</a><br />\n<br />\n上面個post內容係巴打記住我(癲佬)整合 另有原post Credit返：<br />\n突發（上環有大件發生）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1350968\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1350968</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">另外 你班人肯醒未 人地義士用血用汗擋子彈擋煙 你地連罷工都唔肯？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r7mk5G7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr7mk5G7.png&h=27012115&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"735c04f487246f205c90748b51a3cb8a4e3124f7","tid":1351563,"uid":183891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:07:04.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"cec7ecf2c5ffa0830bf782afa99a9eb3285282bb","tid":1351563,"uid":139095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:13:24.000Z","msg":"光復香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"e9d962ec233c19c259729e96617253a13b46b173","tid":1351563,"uid":279357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:13:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><br />\n首先係個七婆對付你<br />\n搞唔掂就搵警察關懷你<br />\n再攪唔掂就搵黑社會欺壓你<br />\n咁我哋都要同佢同步<br />\n游行示威你唔理<br />\n勇武抗爭你打擊我哋<br />\n我地咩都唔怕嘅時候<br />\n你就搵黑社會打無辜嘅市民<br />\n今時今日咁嘅環境<br />\n香港市民重點會安心返工<br />\n我哋係市民<br />\n我哋唔係一個政權嘅工具<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n 罷工罷市<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"9d5e2610bb9711d64b83f39c660280bfa88de585","tid":1351563,"uid":264394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:18:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5f488ff2092d407c77d3ae112325281eacc574cb","tid":1351563,"uid":264394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:18:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7f78ec41e47330ab29b6868c74d5c45594ebc29f","tid":1351563,"uid":264394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:18:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6e1a3e39b682808157bd923ec5f28457e2aa8a4f","tid":1351563,"uid":264394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:19:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f616715655d819642adb1e55944ed093f4e4648a","tid":1351563,"uid":279357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:22:57.000Z","msg":"好好利用恐懼<br />\n等林鄭自己捉蟲<br />\n以為用恐懼可以威脅香港人<br />\n我哋就用呢種威脅<br />\n去令到香港市民罷工罷市<br />\n如果成功佢哋唔會再有一次<br />\n利用呢種手段去威嚇我哋<br />\n我哋要拉商家落嚟<br />\n我哋已經動用晒所有市民嘅資源<br />\n無論係衝擊中聯辦<br />\n定係義士用生命去同黑警抗爭<br />\n我哋香港市民都要陪上佢哋嘅安危<br />\n咁只有用經濟去將呢一個極權嘅政府<br />\n從佢哋高高在上嘅位置拉返落嚟<br />\n唔要一個管治型嘅政府<br />\n香港人需要嘅事服務型嘅政府"},{"pid":"89c5fab8a8a49fd4083acb685ae6f6eeb761da33","tid":1351563,"uid":259381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:24:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a7b629a5c9c6bb2501e15f0c8cb626686a7dc7dd","tid":1351563,"uid":259381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:25:04.000Z","msg":"推！！！"},{"pid":"11e17b172f81cb8dc3ff9e708e068c51d36ee8d5","tid":1351563,"uid":71037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:41:05.000Z","msg":"國難當前，人肉置頂"},{"pid":"c535998f8126ff49987c3a07b8e280f9c18de071","tid":1351563,"uid":71037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:41:35.000Z","msg":"國難當前，人肉置頂"},{"pid":"4e4d685a5073a2a3640470aaba2bd170842698ae","tid":1351563,"uid":71037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:43:04.000Z","msg":"國難當前，人肉置頂"},{"pid":"5ee7c6ea88b3bc07c345859964e551442d1d8fdf","tid":1351563,"uid":71037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:43:28.000Z","msg":"國難當前，人肉置頂"},{"pid":"baf025021a421a8121b390e1396516df6a6c780f","tid":1351563,"uid":10070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:47:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}